Lockdown seems to be unraveling so many issues couples face, the case of Aman Srivastsva is not any different. Aman Srivastava has divorced his wife after learning to cook almost everything during this lockdown. Aman who was previously not a good cook never complained about the food and ate everything that his wife cooked. Meanwhile Aman has now  learnt the perfect way of cooking, he wants to live freely without any hassles. Hence leading to divorcing his wife. Neighbors were very angry with Aman and even accused him of being an evil person. But then Aman invited them all to diner which would have been cooked by his wife the neighbors who already knew the taste of the food declined and supported Aman in getting the divorce. According to reports, Aman’s neighbors have also filed for divorce after getting inspired from Aman’s story.